        "timestamp": "2020-10-07 13:46:31.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\nYou don't need that.. as I updated docs\n\nsimply run: mvn clean install -Pdocker -Pdocker.skip.push=true\n\nAbove will create docker image but will not push to any docker-repo",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
